---
import ButtonPrimary from '../../components/ButtonPrimary.astro';
import Eyebrow from '../../components/Eyebrow.astro';
import Frame from '../../components/Frame.astro';
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../../components/SectionHeading.astro';

const operatingAreas = [
	'lead generation',
	'prospect information and preparation',
	'controlled outreach sends',
	'bounce monitoring',
	'rejection and opt-out handling',
	'reply monitoring',
	'Telegram alerts where attention is needed',
	'human review and approval',
	'booked meeting handoff into CRM',
	'follow-up tasks and reminders',
	'relationship notes',
	'business activity visibility',
	'RAG context',
	'system health checks',
];

const phases = [
	{
		title: 'Prepare',
		steps: ['Lead generation', 'Prospect information prepared', 'Controlled outreach sent'],
	},
	{
		title: 'Protect',
		steps: ['Bounces monitored', 'Rejections handled', 'Opt-outs protected'],
	},
	{
		title: 'Review',
		steps: ['Replies monitored', 'Telegram alerts raised', 'Human approval kept in the loop'],
	},
	{
		title: 'Follow through',
		steps: ['Meeting booked', 'CRM handoff', 'Follow-up controlled'],
	},
];
---

<Layout
	title="Kalyan AI Internal Operating Stack | Kalyan AI"
	description="A live internal operating system used by Kalyan AI to manage commercial activity, follow-up, business visibility and system health from one controlled place."
	showFinalCta={false}
>
	<section class="case-hero">
		<div class="ka-wrap">
			<div class="case-hero__grid">
				<div>
					<Eyebrow tone="dark">Internal proof system</Eyebrow>
					<h1>Kalyan AI Internal Operating Stack</h1>
					<p>Kalyan AI's own controlled operating system for lead generation, outreach, replies, CRM, business visibility, RAG, system health and owner control.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="case-hero__panel">
					<span>Controlled operating proof</span>
					<strong>The same principle Kalyan AI applies for clients, applied to its own business.</strong>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="ka-section ka-section-white">
		<div class="ka-wrap">
			<div class="case-two-col">
				<SectionHeading
					eyebrow="Why we built it"
					title="Kalyan AI needed the same thing many owner-led businesses need."
					highlight="many owner-led businesses need."
				/>
				<div class="case-copy">
					<p>Kalyan AI needed a clearer way to see what is happening, what needs attention, what is moving forward and what is slipping.</p>
					<p>Instead of relying on scattered tools, inboxes, memory and disconnected spreadsheets, we built an internal operating system around how the business actually works.</p>
					<p>The aim was simple: keep lead generation, outreach, replies, booked meetings, CRM follow-up, reminders, business activity, RAG context and system health visible in one controlled place.</p>
					<p>This is not a demo system. It is the live operating stack Kalyan AI uses to manage its own commercial activity.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="ka-section ka-section-paper">
		<div class="ka-wrap">
			<div class="case-built-grid">
				<div>
					<SectionHeading
						eyebrow="What the system brings together"
						title="One operating view for commercial activity."
						highlight="One operating view"
						lead="Behind the scenes, there is technical infrastructure making this work. The important point is that the business has one clear operating view."
					/>
					<ul class="case-feature-list">
						{operatingAreas.map((area) => (
							<li><span></span>{area}</li>
						))}
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="case-frame-stack">
					<Frame
						src="/images/case-studies/kalyan-ai-internal-stack/kalyan-ai-internal-operating-dashboard.png"
						alt="Kalyan AI internal operating dashboard showing commercial activity, follow-up and system health."
						label="Sanitised internal operating dashboard"
						loading="eager"
					/>
					<Frame
						src="/images/case-studies/kalyan-ai-internal-stack/kalyan-ai-outreach-activity-dashboard.png"
						alt="Kalyan AI outreach activity dashboard showing activity trends and follow-up visibility."
						label="Sanitised outreach activity dashboard"
						loading="eager"
					/>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="ka-section ka-section-deep case-flow-band">
		<div class="ka-wrap">
			<SectionHeading
				eyebrow="Commercial flow"
				title="Commercial activity is grouped into controlled phases."
				lead="The stack supports the commercial side of Kalyan AI from preparation through to CRM follow-up, while keeping human judgement in the loop."
				tone="dark"
			/>
			<div class="internal-phase-grid">
				{phases.map((phase, phaseIndex) => (
					<article>
						<span>Phase {phaseIndex + 1}</span>
						<h3>{phase.title}</h3>
						<ul>
							{phase.steps.map((step, stepIndex) => (
								<li>
									<strong>{String(stepIndex + 1).padStart(2, '0')}</strong>
									<p>{step}</p>
								</li>
							))}
						</ul>
					</article>
				))}
			</div>
			<div class="case-dark-note">
				<p>The point is not to remove human control. The point is to keep the right information visible, the right actions tracked, and the right decisions under human review.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="ka-section ka-section-white case-results">
		<div class="ka-wrap">
			<div class="case-results__grid">
				<div>
					<SectionHeading
						eyebrow="What this proves"
						title="Systems should be built around the business, not the other way round."
						highlight="around the business"
					/>
					<div class="case-copy">
						<p>This internal system proves the same principle Kalyan AI applies for clients: understand how the business actually works, find where visibility is weak, and build a practical system around a real operating need.</p>
						<p>For Kalyan AI, that means commercial activity, outreach, replies, meetings, CRM follow-up, reminders, RAG context and system health.</p>
						<p>For another business, it may be bookings, finance, customer communication, operations, reporting or delivery control. The system changes depending on the business. The principle stays the same.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="case-proof-panel">
					<Eyebrow>Built with control</Eyebrow>
					<h3>Clear boundaries, human approval and ongoing monitoring.</h3>
					<p>The system is operated with clear boundaries, human approval, source-of-truth ownership and ongoing monitoring.</p>
					<p>It is built around the idea that the right information should be visible and the right decisions should stay under human control.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="ka-section ka-section-paper case-cta">
		<div class="ka-wrap">
			<div class="case-cta__inner">
				<Eyebrow>Start here</Eyebrow>
				<h2>Want to find the right first system for your business?</h2>
				<p>The Business AI Blueprint is a focused paid review that helps identify where AI can create real value, what system is worth building first, and whether there is a clear business case before a larger build.</p>
				<ButtonPrimary href="/blueprint" label="Start with the Business AI Blueprint" data-plausible="BookACall" />
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.case-hero {
		background:
			linear-gradient(100deg, rgba(8, 20, 40, 0.98) 22%, rgba(8, 20, 40, 0.76) 62%, rgba(8, 20, 40, 0.98) 100%),
			radial-gradient(circle at 80% 24%, rgba(0, 183, 198, 0.22), transparent 34%),
			var(--navy-deep);
		color: var(--white);
	}

	.case-hero__grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 0.75fr;
		gap: 64px;
		align-items: end;
		padding: 116px 0 132px;
	}

	.case-hero h1 {
		max-width: 14ch;
		margin: 0 0 24px;
		color: var(--white);
		font-size: clamp(46px, 6vw, 76px);
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.case-hero p {
		max-width: 56ch;
		color: var(--body-light);
		font-size: 18px;
		line-height: 1.66;
	}

	.case-hero__panel {
		padding: 30px;
		border: 1px solid var(--line-dark);
		border-radius: 16px;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		text-align: left;
	}

	.case-hero__panel span {
		color: var(--teal-soft);
		font-family: "JetBrains Mono", ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
		font-size: 11px;
		letter-spacing: 0.09em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	.case-hero__panel strong {
		display: block;
		margin-top: 14px;
		color: var(--white);
		font-family: "Fraunces", Georgia, serif;
		font-size: clamp(28px, 3vw, 42px);
		font-weight: 600;
		line-height: 1.08;
	}

	.case-two-col,
	.case-built-grid,
	.case-results__grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
		gap: 64px;
		align-items: start;
	}

	.case-copy {
		display: grid;
		gap: 18px;
		max-width: 58ch;
		color: var(--body);
		font-size: 17px;
		line-height: 1.68;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.case-feature-list {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 14px;
		margin: 34px 0 0;
		padding: 0;
		list-style: none;
	}

	.case-feature-list li {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 16px 1fr;
		gap: 12px;
		padding: 18px;
		border: 1px solid var(--line-light);
		border-radius: 14px;
		background: var(--white);
		color: var(--body);
		font-size: 15px;
		line-height: 1.55;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.case-feature-list span {
		width: 8px;
		height: 8px;
		margin-top: 0.62em;
		border-radius: 999px;
		background: var(--teal);
	}

	.case-frame-stack {
		display: grid;
		gap: 22px;
	}

	.case-flow-band {
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.case-flow-band::before {
		content: "";
		position: absolute;
		inset: auto -8% -30% 48%;
		height: 520px;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 183, 198, 0.14), transparent 68%);
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	.internal-phase-grid {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
		gap: 18px;
		margin-top: 58px;
	}

	.internal-phase-grid article {
		padding: 24px;
		border: 1px solid var(--line-dark);
		border-radius: 16px;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
		text-align: left;
	}

	.internal-phase-grid article > span {
		color: var(--teal-soft);
		font-family: "JetBrains Mono", ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
		font-size: 11px;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	.internal-phase-grid h3 {
		margin: 12px 0 20px;
		color: var(--white);
		font-size: 24px;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.internal-phase-grid ul {
		display: grid;
		gap: 14px;
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
		list-style: none;
	}

	.internal-phase-grid li {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 38px 1fr;
		gap: 12px;
	}

	.internal-phase-grid strong {
		display: flex;
		width: 36px;
		height: 36px;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		border: 1px solid rgba(63, 216, 227, 0.34);
		border-radius: 10px;
		background: rgba(0, 183, 198, 0.10);
		color: var(--teal-soft);
		font-family: "JetBrains Mono", ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
		font-size: 12px;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.internal-phase-grid p,
	.case-dark-note p {
		color: var(--body-light);
		font-size: 14px;
		line-height: 1.58;
	}

	.case-dark-note {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
		max-width: 64ch;
		margin-top: 46px;
		padding-top: 28px;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--line-dark);
	}

	.case-proof-panel,
	.case-cta__inner {
		border: 1px solid var(--line-light);
		border-radius: 16px;
		background: var(--white);
		box-shadow: 0 28px 58px -48px rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.28);
		text-align: left;
	}

	.case-proof-panel {
		padding: 30px;
	}

	.case-proof-panel h3 {
		margin: 0 0 16px;
		color: var(--ink);
		font-size: clamp(28px, 3vw, 40px);
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.case-proof-panel p {
		margin-top: 14px;
		color: var(--body);
		font-size: 16px;
		line-height: 1.66;
	}

	.case-cta__inner {
		max-width: 56ch;
		padding: 34px;
	}

	.case-cta h2 {
		margin: 0 0 18px;
		color: var(--ink);
		font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 44px);
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.case-cta p {
		margin-bottom: 28px;
		color: var(--body);
		font-size: 16px;
		line-height: 1.66;
	}

	@media (max-width: 1040px) {
		.internal-phase-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 860px) {
		.case-hero__grid,
		.case-two-col,
		.case-built-grid,
		.case-results__grid,
		.case-feature-list {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.case-hero__grid {
			padding: 78px 0 92px;
		}

		.internal-phase-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.case-hero__panel,
		.internal-phase-grid article,
		.case-proof-panel,
		.case-cta__inner {
			padding: 22px;
		}
	}
</style>
